NAME
    Acme::Vuvuzela - the glorious sound of the vuvuzela

VERSION
    version 0.04

SYNOPSIS
      use Acme::Vuvuzela;

DESCRIPTION
    Acme::Vuvuzela adds the glorious sound of the vuvuzela to your perl
    programs.

    Simply load the module into your scripts for instant vuvuzela
    experience.

FUNCTIONS
    In case the vuvuzela experience is too much, there is a handy function
    available:

    "KILL"
        Stops the vuvuzela dead.

          Acme::Vuvuzela::KILL;

SEE ALSO
    <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vuvuzela>

